[00:51:43.000 --> 00:51:44.000]  唱出來講出來
[00:51:44.000 --> 00:51:47.000]  We have an unspeakable joy
[00:51:47.000 --> 00:51:49.000]  overwhelming in our hearts
[00:51:49.000 --> 00:51:50.000]  奉耶穌的名祈禱
[00:51:50.000 --> 00:51:51.000]  Amen
